30 April - Lemon Zest Garlic 

- Zest from 2 lemons
- 3 large garlic cloves, minced
- 3/4 cup minced fresh parsley 
- 1 lb angel hair pasta
- 3 tablespoon olive oil
- 1 teaspoon salt
- 6 tablespoon parmesean cheese

Grate zest and combine with garlic and parsely, set aside. Cook pasta. In large frying pan warm oil over medium heat add zest mixture salt and pepper to taste. Cook 1 minute. Do not allow garlic to brown. Toss cooked pasta with mix. Set aside. Add cheese.